  {"id": "seg_00427", "translation": " is the derivative of "},
  {"id": "seg_00428", "translation": "."},
  {"id": "seg_00429", "translation": "Mastering Calculus"},
  {"id": "seg_00430", "translation": "Clearly, x² + C is not a single function but a family of functions. From this, the following conclusion is self-evident."},
  {"id": "seg_00431", "translation": "If "},
