  {"id": "seg_00457", "translation": "Chapter 4 | What Are Derivatives Good For?"},
  {"id": "seg_00458", "translation": "For easy reference, here are the basic functions and their corresponding antiderivatives. Feel free to take this with you!"},
  {"id": "seg_00459", "translation": "Ten \"essential\" formulas in all — memorize them forwards and backwards, and you'll have everything you need to navigate the world of antiderivatives!"},
  {"id": "seg_00460", "translation": "In later chapters, you'll discover that these seemingly humble antiderivatives have quite a distinguished pedigree!"},
  {"id": "seg_00461", "translation": "Next, we'll explore the definite integral together! But first, as always, let's consolidate our learning — it's time to do some exercises."},
